headline: Corpay Cross-Border Launches USCIS Navigator
summary: TORONTO, November 24, 2025--Corpay, Inc. (NYSE: CPAY), a global leader in corporate payments, today announced the launch of USCIS Navigator, an automated payment solution designed to help U.S. immigration law firms securely and efficiently process payments to the U.S. Citizenship and Immigration Services (USCIS).
